{
  "stem": "1918.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 274.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then my poor father went back to Washington again, trying to get papers to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that took another year and a half or so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we finally got those papers, and I think they were-- they were good for toilet paper because Hitler had already marched into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they did everything to block his way from saving his family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And most of us perished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so did he a few years after we got here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a brokenhearted man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did your mother talk about him?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the time that she-- [INAUDIBLE] that he's doing everything and that she missed him terribly because whatever the arranged marriage originally was-- certainly wasn't probably falling in love, but arranged by two families-- at this point in her life she was missing her partner with whom she had all these children.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was desperate for him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What was the ghetto like that was set up in Kisvarda?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was set up-- you probably heard this from other people, but what the-- the system was that the people from the small villages, the hamlets, were brought into the big city, which was Kisvarda-- countless number of villagers.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some village that had only five Jews and some had 20 and were brought into this big city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Little did we know that it was all designed for the purpose of-- when it comes to the big showdown, they will not have to pluck out each Jew from every village, but they'll all be concentrated in this big city called Kisvarda.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they brought them in, and the word was always that it's only from towns or villages where the population is only so many hundreds of thousands or whatever.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
